main event: On 25 Mar 53, an unidentified flying object was sighted near Rabat, French Morocco by Air Force members, confirmed through radar and visual observation for approximately 15 minutes.
interesting points: The object was observed at a high speed of approximately 300 knots,It appeared to maneuver erratically, changing course and altitude rapidly,The object was described as a brilliant white light,The sighting was reported by experienced Air Force personnel,No other aircraft were reported in the vicinity at the time of the sighting.
witness description: 1st Lt. USAF, radar operator at Nouasseur Naval Station
